# Report
This folder contains the complete Final Year Project report.

## Project Title
PM2.5 Forecasting in Johor Using ARIMA and SARIMA models

## Description
The report presents the development and evaluation of ARIMA and SARIMA models for forecasting PM2.5 concentrations across eight monitoring stations in Johor, Malaysia.

The study includes:
- Data preprocessing
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Stationarity testing
- ARIMA and SARIMA modelling
- Residual diagnostics
- Forecast accuracy evaluation using RMSE, MAE and MAPE
- 14-day PM2.5 forecasting

The complete academic report is provided below.
